Bert Gaudet, RHI - offers BILINGUAL SERVICE (French/English)
Canadian Residential Inspection Services raises the bar in the home inspection industry when it comes to professionalism, code of ethics and conduct. All our home inspectors receive intensive training and on-going support to ensure you receive a thorough, unbiased, professional home inspection. Canadian Residential Inspection Services has the most user-friendly, comprehensive home inspection reporting system in the industry.

When you choose Canadian you receive your home inspection report on-site at the time of the inspection as well as a personal consultation with the home inspector.
